---
title: Chicken Sausage Rigatoni Napoletano with Peas, Chili Flakes & Creamy Garlic Sauce
description: A bowl of pasta never fails to satisfy—it’s quick, carby, comforting, and our total go-to for a cozy meal. When you add sweet Italian chicken sausage, green peas, tomato, and Parmesan to the equation, you’ve reached another level of deliciousness entirely. Ready to enjoy bite after bite of al dente rigatoni cloaked in a creamy, dreamy lemon garlic sauce? We thought so.
